main event: Three unidentified objects were spotted hovering over water in Florida in 1964.
interesting points: The objects were reported to be hovering at an altitude of approximately 500 feet.
The objects emitted a bright light at intervals.
The objects suddenly accelerated at high speeds and disappeared upwards over the water.
There were multiple sightings of similar objects reported in the Mulberry, Florida area during the early evening hours.
The witness suggested that a surveillance camera be set up to capture evidence of these unidentified objects.
